# Sacks Law Firm Website

Professional website for Sacks Law Firm - Johannesburg attorneys and conveyancers.

## Features
- SEO optimized with structured data
- Mobile-responsive design
- Single-page navigation
- Contact form ready for Netlify
- Crawl-friendly for search engines

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Customize Content
Edit `index.html` and replace:
- Phone numbers: `011 123 4567`
- Email: `info@sackslaw.co.za`
- Address: `123 Sandton City, 2nd Floor`
- Attorney names and bios
- Image URLs (update Unsplash links to your own photos)

### 2. Update Domain
In these files, replace `sackslaw.co.za` with your actual domain:
- `index.html` (lines 9, 13, 17, 22, 27)
- `robots.txt` (line 3)
- `sitemap.xml` (line 8)

### 3. Add Images
1. Create folder: `images/`
2. Add your photos:
   - `hero.jpg` (1920x1080)
   - `office.jpg` (800x600)
   - `team.jpg` (1000x667)
   - `logo.png` (300x100)
3. Update image `src` attributes in `index.html`

### 4. Deploy to GitHub

#### Method A: GitHub Web Interface
1. Create new repository at github.com
2. Click "Upload files"
3. Drag & drop all 4 files
4. Commit changes

#### Method B: Git Commands
```bash
# Initialize repository
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Sacks Law Firm website"

# Connect to GitHub
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/YOUR-REPO.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main